4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in JavaScript and Python. Over 18 weeks, participants engage in three weekly classes, benefiting from a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. The curriculum covers web development, algorithm scripting, API utilization, and culminates in a personal project to gain practical experience. No prior coding experience is required, and classes are available in both English and Spanish. Graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate, enhancing their job prospects in the tech industry. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop